  "instructions": [
    "Soak the red lentils in water for 30 minutes before cooking.",
    "Drain the water and boil the lentils in 2 cups of water until they are tender.",
    "Heat the mustard oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and coriander seeds to the pan and let them sizzle.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger to the pan and sauté until they are softened.",
    "Add the red chili and turmeric to the pan and sauté for another minute.",
    "Add the almond and salt to the pan and mix well.",
    "Add the cooked lentils to the pan and mix well.",
    "Garnish with fresh cilantro and serve hot."
